            <title>Dresser-Rand, Gaelectric Form Alliance to Develop CAES Projects</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	Dresser-Rand Group Inc. recently announced a strategic alliance with Gaelectric to develop compressed air energy storage (CAES) projects in Europe. Under the agreement, Gaelectric and Dresser-Rand will collaborate on the design, development, engineering, procurement and commissioning of European CAES projects.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Initially, Gaelectric and Dresser-Rand will work together on an advanced CAES project near Larne, Northern Ireland. When completed the Larne CAES project will include a 268-megawatt twin power train storage and electricity generation facility. The total investment of the project is estimated to be up to $476 million with a target commissioning date of 2017.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Dresser-Rand&amp;#39;s initial scope of supply will include project management, scheduling and technical support services through the planning phase of the Larne project, including front-end engineering and design in 2014. Full project release is expected at the end of 2014.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	&amp;quot;We are very excited about the opportunity to work with Gaelectric as a strategic alliance partner and on the Larne CAES project specifically,&amp;quot; said Jerry Walker, Dresser&amp;shy;Rand executive vice president for global solutions. &amp;quot;Gaelectric has a strong commitment to Northern Ireland as a leading independent developer of wind energy projects and a clear understanding and commitment to energy storage as the essential enabler in integrating large amounts of renewables on to power systems across Europe.&amp;quot;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Among the largest suppliers of rotating equipment solutions to the oil, gas, petrochemical and process industries, Dresser-Rand operates manufacturing facilities in the United States, France, the United Kingdom, Spain, Germany, Norway and India with a network of 49 service and support centers covering more than 150 countries.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	For information, visit &lt;a href="http://www.dresser-rand.com"&gt;www.dresser-rand.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/energy_management/~4/SZEz5w2mV1Q" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
