            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:1278b144-5512-4761-9106-9e6100deea8b</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/energy_management/~3/hlS_godXA7s/Environmental-progress-electronics-industry</link>
