            <category>Media Entries</category>
            <title>Tour of Erickson Power Plant in Lansing, Mich.</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	Lansing (Mich.) Board of Water and Light&amp;#39;s Erickson Coal Plant was down for repair recently. This provided an opportunity to tour the facility and access stuff you can&amp;#39;t normally see/touch.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/energy_management/~4/Hn9NJzzCLLY" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
