            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:bcc1a80b-097c-46fd-a11e-9e3000993522</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/energy_management/~3/7o7-znwpW6g/GE-winners-ecomagination-challenge</link>
