	* Read the &lt;a href="http://www.electrificationcoalition.org/news-ec-praises-ge-electric-vehicle-announcement.php" jquery1289920066906="17"&gt;Coalition&amp;rsquo;s statement&lt;/a&gt; in support of GE&amp;rsquo;s fleet purchase announcement&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/energy_management/~4/Cv7JoJ4Png4" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
