            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:ea273df8-ffe0-4930-a1e2-9e2c00e7513b</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/energy_management/~3/DnRsKbaCcGA/General-Mills-sustainability-goals</link>
