	* View our &lt;a href="http://www.gereports.com/driving-down-ev-memory-lane-a-look-back-at-ges-test-models/" jquery1288898114031="11"&gt;gallery of GE&amp;rsquo;s past EV test projects&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
	* See &lt;a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7XqrdDuDgEU" jquery1288898114031="12"&gt;video interview with Bob in our EV lab&lt;/a&gt; from 2008&lt;br /&gt;
	* Read an &lt;a href="http://inspiredeconomist.com/2009/05/01/ge-shows-the-way-forward-with-advanced-electric-and-hybrid-vehicles/" jquery1288898114031="13"&gt;The Inspired Economist&amp;rsquo;s interview with Bob King&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
