            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:dae99ed8-a173-491f-8922-9e170076f5a9</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/energy_management/~3/QWr5ozBy5WQ/Green-car-of-year-finalists</link>
