            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:af5f4efe-f390-45d1-9ef7-9e17006cc8d4</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/energy_management/~3/vzxjTnjv1pU/Raytheon-America-green-companies</link>
