	* &amp;ldquo;&lt;a href="http://www.gereports.com/ge-better-place-to-partner-on-ev-infrastructure/" jquery1287668288811="16"&gt;GE &amp;amp; Better Place to partner on EV infrastructure&lt;/a&gt;&amp;rdquo;&lt;br /&gt;
	* &amp;ldquo;&lt;a href="http://www.gereports.com/unveiled-200m-challenge-ev-charger-smart-monitor/" jquery1287668288811="17"&gt;Unveiled: $200M challenge, EV charger, smart monitor&lt;/a&gt;&amp;rdquo;&lt;br /&gt;
	* &amp;ldquo;&lt;a href="http://www.gereports.com/ge-teams-with-nissan-on-electric-car-smart-charging/" jquery1287668288811="18"&gt;GE teams with Nissan on electric car smart charging&lt;/a&gt;&amp;rdquo;&lt;br /&gt;
	* &amp;ldquo;&lt;a href="http://www.gereports.com/new-york-powers-up-with-new-ge-battery-plant/" jquery1287668288811="19"&gt;New York powers up with new GE battery plant&lt;/a&gt;&amp;rdquo;&lt;br /&gt;
	* &amp;ldquo;&lt;a href="http://www.gereports.com/in-1917-electric-vehicles-reigned-and-edison-charged-them/" jquery1287668288811="20"&gt;In 1900 Electric Vehicles Reigned and Edison Charged Them!&lt;/a&gt;&amp;ldquo;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/energy_management/~4/pw6SS-J5meU" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
