            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:4dbb483e-4fe4-41d9-aa8f-9e1500e8990f</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/energy_management/~3/nJOe2QVTqmo/Honda-issues-environmental-report</link>
