            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:32852cc7-6190-48a6-ad32-9e150067d520</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/energy_management/~3/LEVPVzbTXHc/SKF-LEED-green-building</link>
